   <note type="biography">
      <p>Birth: Kirkintilloch, Dunbartonshire, Scotland (11 April 1776)</p>
      <p>Death: 11 February 1847</p>
      
      <p>Profession: Editor</p>
      <p>Education: Edinburgh University; Glasgow University</p>
      <p>Career: Librarian to the Writers of the signet (1805); edited a supplement to the 6th edition of Encyclopaedia Britannica (1814-1824) and edited the 7th edition (1827-1842); Editor, Edinburgh Review (1829); Clerk of Session, Edinburgh (1837)</p>
      <p>Memberships: Society of Writers (1799, admitted by signet)</p>
      
      <p>Membership: Fellow</p>
      <p>Election Date: 12/06/1817</p>
   </note>
